\plain \b \f1 \fs20 \cf0 State of Missouri, ex rel., Sunshine Enterprises of Missouri, Inc., d/b/a/ Sunshine Title and Check Advance, Appellant, v. Board of Adjustment of the City of St. Ann, and City of St. Ann, Respondents.
\par \pard \ltrpar\li0 \fi0 \ri0 \sl240 \sb0 \sa0 \par \pard \ltrpar\li0 \fi0 \ri0 \sl240 \sb0 \sa0 \plain \b \f1 \fs20 \cf4 Case Number:  
